FYI:  The draft Electric Supply and Transmission Act ("the Barton bill") being debated in the U.S. Congress proposes to make the following changes to BPA:


?	The Bonneville Power Administration (BPA) transmission system is brought under FERC jurisdiction and authorized to participate in an RTO.  BPA may engage in retail sales only to certain existing customers.  